This class shows all distributed test names. They will be used to identify the requested configuration file into the main properties file, as the mainPropertyName parameter on the simulator initialization by GenericApp.start(...) method or its constructors.

The name structure has been designed following the test name, deleting the common starting planet.test and using an underscore to separate each subpackage name. For example, the main test class planet.test.SimTest has its name as SIMTEST, and for planet.test.GML.GMLTopology.GMLTopologyTest has GML_GMLTOPOLOGY_GMLTOPOLOGYTEST. In this way, any test has an unique property key.
